description:
Is the Bible literally true, every story, every word? What do we believe as Adventists on how we should read the Bible? What happens when the Bible doesn’t line up exactly with the history and science we understand today? Find answers to these questions and much more in this newest episode of ANN In-Depth. 

For this episode, we are joined by Ty Gibson. Ty is the Director of Light Bearers and pastor of Storyline Adventist Church in Eugene, Oregon. He teaches on a variety of topics, emphasizing God’s unfailing love as the central theme of the Bible.
